      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 560,
        "height": 496,
        "content": "# üí¨ AI Chat Bot ‚Äî Telegram + AIMLAPI (via n8n)\n\nThis workflow lets users chat with **GPT-5** directly in Telegram. Messages are processed and answered in real-time via **AIMLAPI**.\n\n---\n\n## üöÄ Features\n\n* Chat with GPT-5 using natural language\n* Context-aware conversation\n* Telegram delivery of responses\n* Easy to extend with logging or moderation"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "1d3c2472-92fe-4d4e-b157-81de61882d0b",
      "name": "Sticky Note ‚Äî Customization",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1168,
        816
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 560,
        "height": 560,
        "content": "## ‚öôÔ∏è Customization\n\n* Change the `model` parameter to use other AI models (Claude, Gemini, etc.)\n* Add:\n  * Message logging to Google Sheets or DB\n  * NSFW filtering\n  * Command handling (`/help`, `/reset`)\n\n---\n\n## üí° Example User Flow\n\n1. User sends:\n   ```\n   What's the capital of Japan?\n   ```\n2. Bot replies:\n   > The capital of Japan is Tokyo.\n\n3. Chat continues naturally with context preserved"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "fc3443dd-7c1d-478f-846b-e20b2d480898",
      "name": "Sticky Note ‚Äî Setup Guide",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1744,
        448
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 560,
        "height": 544,
        "content": "# üõ† Setup Guide\n\n### 1. üì≤ Create a Telegram Bot\n* Go to [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather)\n* Use `/newbot`, set a name and username\n* Save the **API token**\n\n---\n### 2. üîê Connect Telegram API in n8n\n* Go to `Credentials > Telegram API`\n* Create new credentials using the token from BotFather\n\n---\n### 3. üîå Set Up AIMLAPI Credentials in n8n\n* Go to `Credentials > AI/ML API`\n* Enter your **API key**\n* Base URL: `https://api.aimlapi.com/v1`\n* Docs: [docs.aimlapi.com](https://docs.aimlapi.com)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "cdd88b85-4766-4e2c-9e5f-7b409963c443",
