      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 560,
        "height": 432,
        "content": "## üìÅ Optional Data Logging\n\nYou can log every chat message to Google Sheets or a database for analytics:\n\n` | user_id | date | message | response | `\n` | ------- | ---- | ------- | -------- | `\n\n---\n## üß™ Testing Tips\n\n* Use a test Telegram chat before production\n* Add `Console` or `Set` nodes to inspect payloads\n* For realistic tests, run via `/execute` from Telegram, **not** \"Execute Node\""
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
